  "detailed_description": "<h1>Coming soon - Grunn!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Hoppa is a short adventure game about a baby duck that is separated from its mother, could you bring them back?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135190/extras/8be243235faefbb3a425413587ecc961.poster.avif?t=1726497650\" width=302 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135190/extras/8be243235faefbb3a425413587ecc961.webm?t=1726497650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135190/extras/8be243235faefbb3a425413587ecc961.mp4?t=1726497650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> ~5 minutes of gameplay, it's quite short.<br></li><li> A cool jumping mechanic.<br></li><li> Relaxing audio.<br></li><li> Cute ducks.<br></li><li> Funny leg animations.<br></li><li> Almost more achievements than minutes of playtime!</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135190/extras/c350ac25322f0cc81d29044611c576b9.avif?t=1726497650\" width=200 height=70 /></span><br>Sokpop makes a new game every two weeks!<br>Subscribe for 3$ per month at ",
